          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1682354233884-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> falafel mix</strong> and shape into 3 balls per person (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Add the <strong>falafel balls</strong> to one side of a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray, then press down gently to flatten them and shape into discs</p><p>Drizzle the falafel with <strong>olive oil</strong> and bake for an initial 15 min or until golden and firm – these are your <strong>herby falafel</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1682354238026-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
