            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and finely shred</p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> into thin wedges</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your<strong> lemon[s]</strong> into wedges </p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1682354242008-x200.jpg",
