            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>warmed pitta</strong> with <strong>most</strong> of the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>red onion slices</strong>, <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and<strong> herby falafel</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>tahini yoghurt </strong>and your <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>remaining shredded lettuce, red onion slices & tomato wedges </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
